{"tid":1765522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"報道稱中美貿易協議或因香港問題受阻","createTime":"2019-12-02T02:32:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T06:05:06.000Z","uid":125168,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"7f2e1768987c0606850770ddec0e2897d0b6d0d6","tid":1765522,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T02:32:42.000Z","msg":"報道稱中美貿易協議或因香港問題受阻<br />\n<br />\n中美首階段貿易協議可能由於香港問題而受阻延。《路透社》引述美國新聞網站報道，接近總統特朗普的談判團隊成員認為，由於涉及香港的法例問題，導致中美貿易協議受阻。另外，中國國家主席習近平亦需要時間，穩定內部政治，亦令協議受到阻延。中國外交部早前指責，特朗普簽署《香港人權與民主法案》，嚴重干預中國內政。<br />\n<br />\n2019-12-02 10:27:24 RTHK TG"},{"pid":"1ab051598670a70bcf403a44a68cda38276fefef","tid":1765522,"uid":263563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T02:33:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e3d5d1cb65ec910d3eac499dcfb52b7847f9554","tid":1765522,"uid":125168,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T02:33:56.000Z","msg":"咁嘅形勢，香港人呢次唔打到贏為止仲等幾時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df59776f3e402c23507dbc4f61d45ea862c67279","tid":1765522,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T02:34:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3722b2301e784d87cab34fffae6f48f58cd462c3","tid":1765522,"uid":74182,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T02:34:45.000Z","msg":"其實本身都唔知幾時先簽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dac9e85dff07021da98b7a59ec8e95e64b632b2","tid":1765522,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T02:35:16.000Z","msg":"中國國家主席習近平亦需要時間，穩定內部政治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88586b2219a368c467c5e434492d713c9b3bc23e","tid":1765522,"uid":125168,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"3722b2301e784d87cab34fffae6f48f58cd462c3","tid":1765522,"uid